gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Master Dasa Shambhudas Soi; Thar Dhana Ji Same Nah KoI;
This Old Seed Many People, Settles Village Names Pawan.

The two lines translate to:

Double devotee is Valabhai's name, wish-fulfiller Dada Mayaram;
Know the Lord Bhavani Shankar, glorify Rudra Rama Shankar.
